    <item>
      <title>2,000% IPO 背后的新泽西小型经纪商将在中断后回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/tiny-nj-broker-behind-2-000-ipos-set-to-return-after-hiatus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在引领 2022 年全球最疯狂的首次公开募股之后——一上市就飙升13,000%——鲜为人知的券商Network 1 Financial Securities Inc.正准备引导一批微型资本公司登陆美国交易所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/tiny-nj-broker-behind-2-000-ipos-set-to-return-after-hiatus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:45:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>携程首席执行官孙洁在达沃斯接受彭博社采访</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/trip-com-ceo-jane-sun-speaks-with-bloomberg-in-davos-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管房地产等其他经济领域持续面临压力，但中国旅游业的表现“非常好”。携程集团首席执行官孙洁在达沃斯世界经济论坛年会间隙告诉彭博电视台。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/trip-com-ceo-jane-sun-speaks-with-bloomberg-in-davos-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行首席执行官表示欧洲需要资本市场联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/deutsche-bank-ceo-says-europe-needs-capital-market-union-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行首席执行官 Christian Sewing 表示，资本市场的协调“对于为新技术、新兴产业提供融资是必要的”。他在瑞士达沃斯世界经济论坛年会上的小组讨论中发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/deutsche-bank-ceo-says-europe-needs-capital-market-union-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:26:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行莫伊尼汉谈美联储降息、资本规则和招聘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/bofa-s-moynihan-on-fed-rate-cuts-capital-rules-hiring-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官布莱恩·莫伊尼汉 (Brian Moynihan) 讨论了美联储货币政策的前景、他对拟议的巴塞尔协议 III 终局规则的看法以及该银行的招聘计划。他在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛年会上接受彭博电视采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/bofa-s-moynihan-on-fed-rate-cuts-capital-rules-hiring-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:18:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行莫伊尼汉表示，拟议的银行规则需要改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/bofa-s-moynihan-says-proposed-rules-for-us-banks-need-to-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官布赖恩·莫伊尼汉表示，需要改变美国主要银行增加资本的拟议监管改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/bofa-s-moynihan-says-proposed-rules-for-us-banks-need-to-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 17:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行的莫伊尼汉预计两年内降息八次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/bofa-s-moynihan-sees-eight-rate-cuts-over-two-years-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官布赖恩·莫伊尼汉预计美联储将在 2024 年和 2025 年降息四次。他还谈到了房地产市场面临的压力。他在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛年会上接受彭博电视台采访（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/bofa-s-moynihan-sees-eight-rate-cuts-over-two-years-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利将把安赛乐米塔尔旗下的钢铁制造商国有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/italy-is-set-to-nationalize-steelmaker-owned-by-arcelormittal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谈判失败后，总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 领导的政府准备从主要股东安赛乐米塔尔公司 (ArcelorMittal SA) 手中夺取该国最大钢铁制造商的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/italy-is-set-to-nationalize-steelmaker-owned-by-arcelormittal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:22:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾财富基金计划三到四个月内首次投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/maharlika-investment-corporation-president-ceo-rafael-consing-jr-exclusive-at-bbg-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾第一家主权财富基金 Maharlika Investment Corp. 正准备在未来三到四个月内进行首次投资，可能投资于基础设施和能源领域。该基金总裁兼首席执行官拉斐尔·康辛 (Rafael Consing Jr.) 在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛年会上与哈斯琳达·阿明 (Haslinda Amin) 进行了交谈。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-18/maharlika-investment-corporation-president-ceo-rafael-consing-jr-exclusive-at-bbg-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 14:56:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 10 年期收益率走高，股市反弹减弱：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科技推动的股市反弹失去动力，交易员权衡最新的经济信号，并在美联储讲话中寻找有关美联储下一步行动的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 22:54:55 GMT</pubDate>
